cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SD

The paper deals with the extraction of graphs from images of brain tissue using deep learning methods. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the study of neural networks, which suggests that it could belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The use of deep learning methods and graph theory indicates that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves the development of a toolbox, which could suggest that it belongs to cs.SD (Software Engineering).
